name: Cosmos
description: We cannot see or know everything, so imagination has no limits and reality is relative. Infinite are the ways of seeing and feeling. If you want to fly find the way and you will see how you can exceed everything, the limits are only in the mind. Even the craziest thing can be a joke for the world, let yourself go, observe, everything is crazy if you think about it carefully. So, what do you plan to do now?
